== Design Goals

Be simple

- The web equivalent of Lego blocks for building forms
- Embedded images and complex styling kept to a minimum
  - Fast loading and rendering
  - Easy to reskin visual style
  
Be comprehensive

- Design patterns that cover all common CMS interactions
- Componentization of all standard form elements

Be elegant

- Describe everything in high level language
- Conceptual unity across different components
- High quality of typography and visual execution

Be open

- Released under a permissive license
- Embrace all possible ways of extending and implementing these ideas
- Plugins for many different template engines, CMS platforms and app frameworks